  rows:
    - [reduce_class_eq_builtin,
       "reduce.__class__.__name__.__eq__",
       ["builtin_function_or_method"],
       true,
       "functools.reduce.__class__.__name__.__eq__('builtin_function_or_method') == True — reduce is a C builtin from _functoolsmodule.c; its __class__ is the builtin_function_or_method type (same as len, id, etc.); str.__eq__('builtin_function_or_method') returns True; new to extra159"]
    - [reduce_module_eq__functools,
